Last but not least, we added an interior wedge so you're not completely one with the ground.

Luxury you can feel on the skin…Super-transparent soft tights with incredibly smooth, matt look.
Excellent stretch and a perfect fit, thanks to the use of double-wrapped elastane in each row
Soft knitted waistband with the Wolford logo
Barely visible shadow toe reinforcement
Cotton gusset

name: SLIM FLAGSTONE LONG-SLEEVE TEE
description: We crafted this classic tee in an updated version of our slub cotton—an amazingly soft fabric made from twisted yarns of varying widths that are specially woven to produce a slightly textured look and feel. Not your average tee, its unconventional construction creates a unique "high-low" pattern that makes it a wardrobe all-star in any season. Online only.

name: SLIM-STRAIGHT JEAN IN RESIN CRINKLE WASH
description: Looking for our vintage slim-straight fit? It's now called slim-straight. It's the exact same fit you already know and love—the only thing that's changed is the name. We wash these jeans with a special treatment to give them a great crinkled look. Since they're indigo dyed, they're prone to crocking, or color transfer, so wear (and wash) them with dark colors till they're worn in.

name: Buckley Brogue
description: The Buckley Brogue in bistre is a lace up brogue shoe with classic brogue punch work inspired by a vintage style bought at a London market. This classic style has been constructed using specially sourced leather and designed to provide maximum comfort. Carefully washed and hand burnished for an authentic look, the Buckley Brogue is also available in oxblood and camo .

We constructed ours from supersoft cotton to handle the nine-to-five and the five-to-nine with ease. Rock washed for comfort and a lived-in look and feel, it's cut slimmer than our classic polo but offers a bit more room than our slim fit.
